default as
default being too small (most had fewer than 30 cases), no baseline equivalence between comparator groups, high or 
defaultunequal dr
defaultopout after allocation to groups, and misuse of statistical techniques.
default Seven studies were deemed to be large enough with some attempt at creating a suitable comparator, and so were rated as medium in quality.
default The remaining studies
default were all of low quality with three or more serious flaws.
default 
defaultThere are so few studies of consequence that a traditional meta-analysis is not possible.
